rder border-emerald-500/20 px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded\">{log.status}</span>\n270 |                     </div>\n271 |                   </div>\n272 |                 ))}\n273 |               </div>\n274 |             </div>\n275 | \n276 |           </div>\n277 | \n278 |           {/* Sidebar Area */}\n279 |           <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n280 |             \n281 |             {/* HSM Integrity State Card */}\n282 |             <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n283 |               <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n284 |                 <ShieldCheck className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5 text-green-400\" />\n285 |                 <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">HSM Integrity State</h3>\n286 |               </div>\n287 |               \n288 |               <div className=\"space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n289 |                 <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">\n290 |                   <span>DECAPSULATED:</span>\n291 |                   <span>YES</span>\n292 |                 </div>\n293 |                 <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2 rounded bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">\n294 |                   <span>VERIFICATION:</span>\n295 |                   <span className=\"uppercase\">{doc.status || \"Verified\"}</span>\n296 |                 </div>\n297 |                 <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/70\">\n298 |                   <span>REVISION TIER:</span>\n299 |                   <span>{doc.version}</span>\n300 |                 </div>\n301 |                 <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n302 |                   This document metadata is loaded f